01:09:30.954 --> 01:09:34.930
And I couldn't resist
putting in stuff on the soul

01:09:34.930 --> 01:09:38.873
so I said, look if the
soul has to not, to exist

01:09:38.873 --> 01:09:43.090
after you die, and goes
to heaven, et cetera,

01:09:43.090 --> 01:09:47.800
or the other place, then
it has to, the question is,

01:09:47.800 --> 01:09:51.730
it has to not have anything
that is required by a body.

01:09:51.730 --> 01:09:54.170
So the question is, what
is required by a body?

01:09:54.170 --> 01:09:56.870
And if it's required by a
body, the soul can't have it.

01:09:56.870 --> 01:10:01.200
So you can study the properties
of the soul that way.

01:10:01.200 --> 01:10:02.650
So can the soul see?

01:10:02.650 --> 01:10:03.960
No.

01:10:03.960 --> 01:10:07.347
Hence, can't see, doesn't have
a visual cortex, et cetera.

01:10:07.347 --> 01:10:08.720
Can the soul hear?

01:10:08.720 --> 01:10:13.020
Sorry, doesn't have the
hearing apparatus for that.

01:10:13.020 --> 01:10:15.910
Can the soul feel touch?

01:10:15.910 --> 01:10:16.980
No.

01:10:16.980 --> 01:10:20.970
Doesn't have the appropriate
part of the cortex, et cetera.

01:10:20.970 --> 01:10:22.610
And you go through this list.

01:10:22.610 --> 01:10:24.720
Can the soul remember?

01:10:24.720 --> 01:10:28.163
Doesn't have what is
required for memory for that.

01:10:29.330 --> 01:10:32.443
And so you go through that,
and the next question is,

01:10:32.443 --> 01:10:37.443
does the soul have a
personality or your personality?

01:10:37.850 --> 01:10:40.250
So the question is does personality depend

01:10:40.250 --> 01:10:43.090
upon the brain in any way?

01:10:43.090 --> 01:10:45.831
And this is a question I asked Nina,

01:10:45.831 --> 01:10:49.163
who knows much better than
