01:10:49.163 --> 01:10:53.313
that the Phineas Gage phenomenon would say

01:10:53.313 --> 01:10:56.570
that it's lost control, it
doesn't have inhibition,

01:10:56.570 --> 01:10:59.700
et cetera, sort of like Donald
Trump or you know, (laughs).

01:11:03.790 --> 01:11:07.000
That's certainly one kind
of personality change,

01:11:07.000 --> 01:11:09.790
but also there could be
larger brain injuries

01:11:09.790 --> 01:11:13.580
that could produce sort of
positive changes of all sort

01:11:13.580 --> 01:11:14.830
and if that's the case

01:11:14.830 --> 01:11:18.640
then the soul would not
have a fixed personality

01:11:18.640 --> 01:11:21.400
and therefore not your personality,

01:11:21.400 --> 01:11:24.243
so in what case is it your soul?

01:11:25.836 --> 01:11:28.140
So the question about personality

01:11:28.140 --> 01:11:29.800
is something I really
wanted to ask you about,

01:11:29.800 --> 01:11:31.600
